overview: Feeling blue? Down in the mouth? Has your get up and go got up and went? Well settle back and enjoy some good old-fashioned stand-up comedy buffoonery, courtesy of Christian Finnegan! Recorded live at the Trocadero Theatre in Philadelphia, Au Contraire! is an evening of awkward personal revelations and hypocritical assaults on your character!
tagline: It's hilarious! It's thought-provoking! It's mildly disturbing! It's...Au Contraire!
title: Christian Finnegan: Au Contraire
